Week One – Project Outline (Decentralized Oracle Improvement System)

Day 1–2: Problem Understanding & Domain Study

Understand the oracle problem in blockchain systems

Study existing decentralized oracle solutions and their limitations

Day 3–4: Literature Review & Requirement Analysis

Review research papers, case studies, and real-world oracle networks

Identify functional and non-functional requirements

Day 5: Technology Stack Finalization

Finalize blockchain platform, smart contract language, and tools

Decide oracle architecture and data sources

Day 6: Project Planning

Define project scope, objectives, milestones, and risks

Allocate roles and responsibilities within the team

Day 7: Documentation & Review

Prepare Week 1 documentation and summary report

Review understanding with mentor/guide and refine plan
